iskiyev]]|URS|1976 Summer}}<br />'''L'''  0-5\n|colspan=5|Did not advance\n|- align=center\n|align=left|[[Georgi Stoymenov]]\n|align=left|[[Boxing at the 1976 Summer Olympics|Light Heavyweight]]\n|{{flagIOCathlete|[[Ernesto Sanchez]]|VEN|1976 Summer}}<br />'''W''' 5-0\n|{{flagIOCathlete|[[Janusz Gortat]]|POL|1976 Summer}}<br />'''L'''  AB-3\n|colspan=5|Did not advance\n|- align=center\n|align=left|[[Atanas Suvandzhiev]]\n|align=left|[[Boxing at the 1976 Summer Olympics|Heavyweight]]\n|{{flagIOCathlete|[[Mahmoud Ahmed Ali]]|EGY|1976 Summer}}<br />'''W''' WO\n|{{flagIOCathlete|[[Viktor Ivanov (boxer)|Viktor Ivanov]]|URS|1976 Summer}}<br />'''W''' 4-1\n|{{n/a}}\n|{{flagIOCathlete|[[Mircea \u015eimon]]|ROM|1976 Summer}}<br />'''L''' 1-4\n|colspan=6|Did not advance\n|}\n\n==Canoeing==\n{{main|Canoeing at the 1976 Summer Olympics}}\n\n===Sprint===\n;Men\n{|class=\"wikitable\" style=\"font-size:90%; text-align:center;\"\n|-\n!rowspan=2|Athlete\n!rowspan=2|Event\n!colspan=2|Heats\n!colspan=2|Repechages\n!colspan=2|Semifinals\n!colspan=2|Final\n|- style=\"font-size:95%\"\n!Time\n!Rank\n!Time\n!Rank\n!Time\n!Rank\n!Time\n!Rank\n|-\n|align=left rowspan=2|[[Borislav Ananiev]]\n|align=left|[[Canoeing at the 1976 Summer Olympics \u2013 Men's C-1 500 metres|C-1 500 m]]\n|2:12.16\n|3 '''Q'''\n|colspan=2 {{n/a|BYE}}\n|2:11.23\n|3 '''Q'''\n|1:59.92\n|'''4'''\n|-\n|align=left|[[Canoeing at the 1976 Summer Olympics \u2013 Men's C-1 1000 metres|C-1 1000 m]]\n|4:28.18\n|3 '''Q'''\n|colspan=2 {{n/a|BYE}}\n|4:13.39\n|1 '''Q'''\n|4:14.41\n|'''4'''\n|-\n|align=left rowspan=2|[[Ivan Burchin]]<br />[[Krasimir Khristov]]\n|align=left|[[Canoeing at the 1976 Summer Olympics \u2013 Men's C-2 500 metres|C-2 500 m]]\n|1:58.84\n|2 '''Q'''\n|colspan=2 {{n/a|BYE}}\n|1:51.63\n|2 '''Q'''\n|1:50.43\n|'''6'''\n|-\t\n|align=left|[[Canoeing at the 1976 Summer Olympics \u2013 Men's C-2 1000 metres|C-2 1000 m]]\n|3:57.13\n|4 '''Q'''\n|3:52.00\n|2 '''Q'''\n|3:58.74\n|3 '''Q'''\n|4:02.44\n|'''7'''\n|-\n|align=le