rry|Echeverry]]|COL|1976 Summer}}<br>'''L'''\n|colspan=5|Did not advance\n|}\n\n==Fencing==\n{{main|Fencing at the 1976 Summer Olympics}}\nFive fencers, all men, represented Bulgaria in 1976.\n\n;[[Fencing at the 1976 Summer Olympics \u2013 Men's sabre|Men's sabre]]\n* [[Miroslav Dudekov]]\n* [[Anani Mikhaylov]]\n* [[Trayan Dimitrov]]\n\n;[[Fencing at the 1976 Summer Olympics \u2013 Men's team sabre|Men's team sabre]]\n* [[Miroslav Dudekov]], [[Anani Mikhaylov]], [[Konstantin Dzhelepov]], [[Khristo Khristov]]\n\n==Gymnastics==\n{{main|Gymnastics at the 1976 Summer Olympics}}\n\n==Judo==\n{{main|Judo at the 1976 Summer Olympics}}\n;Men\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"font-size:90%\"\n|-\n!rowspan=\"2\"|Athlete\n!rowspan=\"2\"|Event\n!Round 1\n!Round 2\n!Round 3\n!Round 4\n!Repechage 1\n!Repechage 2\n!colspan=2|Final / {{abbr|BM|Bronze medal match}}\n|- style=\"font-size:95%\"\n!Opposition<br/>Result\n!Opposition<br/>Result\n!Opposition<br/>Result\n!Opposition<br/>Result\n!Opposition<br/>Result\n!Opposition<br/>Result\n!Opposition<br/>Result\n!Rank\n|- align=center\n|align=left|[[Parvan Parvanov]]\n|align=left|[[Judo at the 1976 Summer Olympics|\u221263kg]]\n|{{flagIOCathlete|[[David Saad ]]|LIB|1976 Summer}}<br />'''W''' 0010-0000\n|{{flagIOCathlete|[[Bakhvain Buyadaa]]|MGL|1976 Summer}}<br />'''L''' 0000-0001\n|colspan=5|Did not advance\n|12\n|- align=center\n|align=left|[[Georgi Georgiev (judoka, born 1947)|Georgi Georgiev]]\n|align=left|[[Judo at the 1976 Summer Olympics|\u221270kg]]\n|colspan=1 {{n/a|BYE}}\n|{{flagIOCathlete|[[Vacinuff Morrison]]|GBR|1976 Summer}}<br />'''L''' 0000-0001\n|colspan=5|Did not advance\n|13\n|- align=center\n|align=left|[[Tsancho Atanasov]]\n|align=left|[[Judo at the 1976 Summer Olympics|\u221293kg]]\n|colspan=1 {{n/a|BYE}}\n|{{flagIOCathlete|[[Ung Nam An]]|PRK|1976 Summer}}<br />'''L''' 0000-0010\n|colspan=5|Did not advance\n|18\n|- align=center\n|align=left|[[Emil Petrunov]]\n|align=left|[[Judo at the 1976 Summer Olympics|+93kg]]\n|